- Clear separation between content and footer
- Consistent across all Old Money pages
- Part of "old money" minimalistic design

Implementation:
- HTML: <hr class="footer-divider">
- CSS: 
  .footer-divider {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid #C8C8C8;
